title: Gnarliest Teahupoo Wave Ever -- Nathan Fletcher  #LIVEARNETTE series
description:
In this episode of the #LIVEARNETTE video series, surf legend and XXL Award Winner, Nathan Fletcher, tells a series of events which lead up to surfing one of the gnarliest waves ever caught on film. 

Teahupoo footage provided by: Chris Bryan
